OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780488668
OL,3,CMartin O'Hagan's family urge Police
OL,4,COmbudsman to release report into his
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FThe brother of a man who was shot dead
OL,8,Fby loyalist paramilitaries has called
OL,9,Fon the Police Ombudsman's Office to
OL,10,Fpublish a report into his death after
OL,11,Fthe organisation said it cannot be
OL,12,Freleased until a new Ombudsman is
OL,13,Fappointed.
OL,15,FThe family of Martin O'Hagan - who was
OL,16,Fkilled walking home from a night out
OL,17,Fin Lurgan in 2001 - feel that should
OL,18,Fnot matter.
OL,20,FNo one has ever been convicted of the
OL,21,F51 year-old's murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
