FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780488668
OL,3,CMartin O'Hagan's family urge Police
OL,4,COmbudsman to release report into his
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FFintan O'Hagan said he first
OL,8,Fapproached the Police Ombudsman in
OL,9,F2006 for answers about the police
OL,10,Finvestigation into his brother's
OL,11,Fmurder but he is still waiting on the
OL,12,Freport.
OL,14,F"Five years ago it was imminent. Two
OL,15,Fyears ago it was ready. They contacted
OL,16,Fus in January of this year and said,
OL,17,Fright, 'We're ready to go'", he said.
OL,19,FNow, Mr O'Hagan has been told that
OL,20,Funtil a new Police Ombudsman has been
OL,21,Fhired, the report cannot be published.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780488668
OL,3,CMartin O'Hagan's family urge Police
OL,4,COmbudsman to release report into his
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,F"Then the next Ombudsman will come in
OL,8,Fand he may be brilliant, but then he
OL,9,Fis going to have to get himself all
OL,10,Fover Martin's case.
OL,12,F"He is going to have to get himself up
OL,13,Fto date. You are talking years again.
OL,15,F"It is crazy. It is absolutely
OL,16,Fridiculous that the situation can
OL,17,Fchange within a few months," he told
OL,18,FUTV.
OL,26,@yD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780488668
OL,3,CMartin O'Hagan's family urge Police
OL,4,COmbudsman to release report into his
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FMr O'Hagan looks forward to the day
OL,8,Fthe report is published and he is
OL,9,Fstill determined that full justice be
OL,10,Fserved.
OL,12,F"It is not the be all and end all. It
OL,13,Fis just part of the process and the be
OL,14,Fall and end all is the perpetrators
OL,15,Fgoing to jail and going where they
OL,16,Fdeserve to be," he continued.
OL,18,FAmnesty International have said the
OL,19,Fmurder continues to have a lasting
OL,20,Fimpact on press freedom.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780488668
OL,3,CMartin O'Hagan's family urge Police
OL,4,COmbudsman to release report into his
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,F"Northern Ireland remains the most
OL,8,Fdangerous place in the UK to be a
OL,9,Fjournalist with threats and attacks on
OL,10,Fa very regular basis, including from
OL,11,Fparamilitary groups.
OL,13,F"All of these years on, all of these
OL,14,Fyears of supposed peace.
OL,16,F"The fact that not only has nobody
OL,17,Fever been held to account for the
OL,18,Fmurder of Martin O'Hagan, but also
OL,19,Fthat the threats and attacks continue
OL,20,Ftoday should be of deep concern to
OL,21,Fanybody who cares about press freedom."
OL,26,@}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
