PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780488668
OL,3,CMartin O'Hagan's family urge Police
OL,4,COmbudsman to release report into his
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FIn a letter to the O'Hagan family, the
OL,8,FChief Executive of the Police
OL,9,FOmbudsman said that he considers it
OL,10,F"both appropriate and important that
OL,11,Freports of this significance are
OL,12,Fissued by a sitting Police Ombudsman,
OL,13,Fwith the full authority that comes
OL,14,Ffrom that position".
OL,16,FNearly 25 years on, the O'Hagan family
OL,17,Fare also calling for a public inquiry
OL,18,Finto Martin's death.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@SO]
